{
  "stem": "293.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Supposed to be to the labor camps as a penalty, but they were send-- they sending them to Treblinka or Belsitz or-- or to Chelm or to other places where they were killing them the minute they arrive there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were single people survive like, the Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Buchner one.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was there from exactly-- when the Jewish Council transferred to ghetto, and I was working in the Jewish Council as an assistant, the president, before he was arrested-- because he was arrested few months later-- he asked to join it because they needed the police.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In this time, I figure out this is a obligation and is a moral duty to protect the Jewish community and ghetto, particular, the Germans was-- we were not under jurisdiction of Gestapo in this time.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only under jurisdiction under Schutzpo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's two different branches.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Schutzpolizei, you see?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, you will protect the people from the outside world who would like to come over or steal something or something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was there from March, maybe 15 or-- because I was still working as a assistant to the president, and you have to join it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were about 40 of those policemen, so called.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we have the uniform, sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Coincidentally, I was using my black pants, the officer pants, because I dyed them black, and-- and I have boots, you see?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we have a jacket, regular like this, closed with the buttons here, and we have the armband here-- the Ordnungsdiest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But strange things-- a couple months later-- And a hat, a special hat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Similar what we saw in the movie.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was exactly this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Exactly what I wore, dress.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some-- not everybody has the same uniform.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
